{"tid":1509143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察交幾多稅其實有數計!!!","createTime":"2019-08-26T17:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T11:46:17.000Z","uid":85217,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"432bc4fc4f08f0c94a1e924296750279a5dea060","tid":1509143,"uid":85217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"之前見有巴打被黑警問交幾多稅，為左方便大家所以幫大家整理左堆資訊，費事大家遲下畀人拋窒<br />\n<br />\n計算果陣用左以下假設<br />\n<br />\n1. 全部黑警都係頂薪點(實際無可能全部頂薪點)<br />\n2. 全部黑警都係得基本免稅額(實際上仲會有強姦金扣除同其他免稅額)<br />\n3. 因為可能仲有其他津貼所以總數計多10%<br />\n<br />\n所以個數字絕對已經計多有凸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i46eEEr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi46eEEr.png&h=151cfec9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n根據上面個表大家見到佢地計到盡都係交9.3億稅左右<br />\n<br />\n但佢地準備洗香港人幾錢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AiTVc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AiTVc9.png&h=347a8ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係207億呀!<br />\n<br />\n就算佢地交既稅投入返去，香港人仲要補貼198億， 即係以薪俸稅納稅人總數(1,851,742人) 計算人均係10,693港元，以七百萬人口計算都講緊人均2,829港元啊<br />\n<br />\nThey are really well paid for it!!!<br />\n<br />\n參考:<br />\n<br />\n各職級頂薪點<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/category/police-pay-scale/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fcategory%2Fpolice-pay-scale%2F&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=0d55993d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/category/police-pay-scale/</a><br />\n<br />\n各職級編制人數合計<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/review/review_2017_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Freview%2Freview_2017_tc.pdf&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=4632c2e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/review/review_2017_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n警務人員薪級表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/admin/pay/44.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fadmin%2Fpay%2F44.html&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=e3ec0b22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/admin/pay/44.html</a><br />\n<br />\n稅款計算<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/ese/st_comp_2018_19_budget/cstcfrm.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fese%2Fst_comp_2018_19_budget%2Fcstcfrm.htm&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=0f9b028f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/ese/st_comp_2018_19_budget/cstcfrm.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港警務處2019-20年度預算<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/pdf/chead122.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Fpdf%2Fchead122.pdf&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=d0b35d63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/pdf/chead122.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2017/18年度薪俸稅納稅人總數<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ird.gov.hk/dar/2017-18/table/tc/assessing.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fdar%2F2017-18%2Ftable%2Ftc%2Fassessing.pdf&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=b21800f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/dar/2017-18/table/tc/assessing.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"f77f39cc41a7e6ffb25ee2f0ce72dcd05a81829b","tid":1509143,"uid":33930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=9fe8e5ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=