2017-18/table/tc/assessing.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fdar%2F2017-18%2Ftable%2Ftc%2Fassessing.pdf&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=b21800f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ird.gov.hk/dar/2017-18/table/tc/assessing.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"佢地交幾多都唔關我事<br />\n我又唔係佢地出糧<br />\n公屋又無我份<br />\n公院又無我份<br />\n而家黑警都唔保護我仲打9我<br />\n到底我交稅做乜撚"},{"pid":"207f0c2cec425932794cdf9bd50776669710819d","tid":1509143,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03bd653a18a658eab8fc73c049c92d628dd1a221","tid":1509143,"uid":85217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2fa464097c001262da96601756a6ffa9d80e0f1","tid":1509143,"uid":254594,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"432bc4fc4f08f0c94a1e924296750279a5dea060","tid":1509143,"uid":85217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"之前見有巴打被黑警問交幾多稅，為左方便大家所以幫大家整理左堆資訊，費事大家遲下畀人拋窒<br />\n<br />\n計算果陣用左以下假設<br />\n<br />\n1. 全部黑警都係頂薪點(實際無可能全部頂薪點)<br />\n2. 全部黑警都係得基本免稅額(實際上仲會有強姦金扣除同其他免稅額)<br />\n3. 因為可能仲有其他津貼所以總數計多10%<br />\n<br />\n所以個數字絕對已經計多有凸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i46eEEr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi46eEEr.png&h=151cfec9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n根據上面個表大家見到佢地計到盡都係交9.3億稅左右<br />\n<br />\n但佢地準備洗香港人幾錢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AiTVc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AiTVc9.png&h=347a8ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係207億呀!<br />\n<br />\n就算佢地交既稅投入返去，香港人仲要補貼198億， 即係以薪俸稅納稅人總數(1,851,742人) 計算人均係10,693港元，以七百萬人口計算都講緊人均2,829港元啊<br />\n<br />\nThey are really well paid for it!!!<br />\n<br />\n參考:<br />\n<br />\n各職級頂薪點<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/category/police-pay-scale/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fcategory%2Fpolice-pay-sca